{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"93dbb9bc42","title":"中央同意增发退赔款期票的请示","origin":"甘肃省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"226dfa13ea","index":0,"year":1961,"month":4,"day":11,"articleId":"93dbb9bc42"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5c68ce4de7","type":"title","text":"中央同意增发退赔款期票的请示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"93dbb9bc42"},{"id":"3c670e302a","type":"appellation","text":"中共甘肃省委并西北局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"93dbb9bc42"},{"id":"6a8ff277e4","type":"paragraph","text":"三月廿八日电悉。同意你省对一平二调的退赔款增发期票六千四百万元。但是，在发期票的时候，应当由省财政拨给银行六千四百万元，以便明年由银行负责拨款保证期票兑现。同时，在发期票后，要防止各部门和某些单位不积极退赔实物的现象发生。否则，不仅不能更深刻教育干部接受教训，而且也将妨碍政策的彻底贯彻执行。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"93dbb9bc42"},{"id":"fea5bb6bef","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央1961年4月11日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"93dbb9bc42"},{"id":"7e260a673a","type":"paragraph","text":"(甘肃省档案馆91—4—844卷)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"93dbb9bc42"},{"id":"0d54e1d531","type":"appellation","text":"附：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"93dbb9bc42"},{"id":"38f8ee1554","type":"subtitle","text":"中央办公厅机要室赵发同志电话","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"93dbb9bc42"},{"id":"7ffacd2f46","type":"paragraph","text":"1961年4月11日“中央同意增发退赔期票的请示”的电报中，请将“同意你省对一平二调的退赔款增发期票6400万元”一句改为“同意你省对一平二调的退赔款发期票六千四百万元”，请于更正。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"93dbb9bc42"},{"id":"b643449985","type":"paragraph","text":" 接话人：刘淑贞1961年4月21日下午5时半","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"93dbb9bc42"},{"id":"388316bdbf","type":"paragraph","text":"原电为：甘收(61)1186","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"93dbb9bc42"}],"page":{